quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  24,41,"Mbega ntubona yuko Imana ihayagizwa mubiri mu Majuru yose no kw’Isi hamwe n’ibirimwo vyose hamwe n’inyoni mugihe zizinguruye amababa yazo, imwe yose muri izo nyoni ziba zamaze kumenya ugusenga kwazo n’ingene zihayagiza Imana yazo, nayo niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ivyo bagira vyose"
  24,42,"Ubwami bw’Ijuru n’Isi nubw’Imana, noku Mana niho abantu bose bazosubizwayo"
  24,43,"Mbega ntubona yuko Imana ariyo isunika ibicu hanyuma ikavyegeranya bimwe kubindi, mukanya ugaca ubona imvura ivuye murivyo, nayo imanura kuva hejuru y’imisozi yivyo bicu imvura y’urubura igashikira kuwo yishakiye canke nukudashikira kuwo yishakiye, hakaba hegereje umuco w’umuravyo wayo wohumisha amaso"
  24,44,"Imana niyo ihindura Ijoro n’Umutaga, ntankeka muri ivyo vyose harimwo ivyemezo ku bantu bafise amaso"
  24,45,"N’Imana niyo yaremye ibikoko vyose ikoresheje amazi, n’ibindi murivyo bigendesha inda zavyo, n’ibindi navyo bigira kumaguru abiri, n’ibindi navyo bigira kumaguru ane, Imana rero irema uko yishakiye mu vy’ukuri niyo ifise ubushobozi bw’ibintu vyose"
  24,46,"Mu vy’ukuri nitwebwe twamanuye aya majambo y’Imana matagatifu y’ukuri agaragaza ibikenewe vyose biri mw’idini ry’ukuri, n’Imana niyo irongora uwo yishakiye munzira igororotse"
  24,47,"Nabo bavuga bati:- turemeye Imana hamwe n’intumwa yayo kandi turi abagamburutsi munyuma y’ivyo vyose, rero abo simu bantu bemera na gatoyi"
  24,48,"No mugihe bahamagawe kubera Imana yabo y’ukuri hamwe n’intumwa yayo kugira ngo ibacire urubanza ruri hagati yabo, bamwe muribo baca bayahakana"
  24,49,"Niba ukuri ari rwabo, baca baza iwe n’ubugamburutsi ntangere"
  24,50,"Mbega barafise ingwara mumitima yabo, canke barafise amakenga canke batinya yuko Imana izoba hemukira hamwe n’intumwa yayo, ahubwo nibo bahemukiye imitima yabo"